    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. While the engine and transmission are solid, the car shows clear signs of age, including noticeable paint fading on the hood and some interior wear on the upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical items that will need attention soon, such as worn brake pads and a slow window motor, but it remains safe and road-legal. This is a great option for someone willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
