      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously preserved and showing no signs of wear, the exterior finish is flawless, complemented by an interior that remains in a pristine, factory-original state. Having undergone a comprehensive mechanical certification, this unit offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. We invite serious inquiries for this exceptional automotive investment.",
