      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this absolute beauty in person. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly in pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or spill to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I'm honestly a little heartbroken to let it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have!",
      "price": 43500.0,
