    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman, finished in a deep Jet Black Metallic that looks like glass thanks to a professional multi-stage paint correction and high-grade ceramic coating. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. The interior is equally impeccable; the Black leather sport seats show zero bolster wear, and the cabin remains entirely smoke-free, retaining its original factory scent. Every surface, from the Alcantara headliner to the brushed aluminum trim, is free of scratches, scuffs, or oils. Mechanically, this vehicle is in peak form, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by authorized Porsche technicians. It comes equipped with the Premium Package, 20-inch Carrera S wheels, and a crisp Bose Surround Sound System. The sale includes all original keys, the window sticker, and a clean CARFAX report. I strongly encourage any independent pre-purchase inspection to verify its flawless state. This is a collector-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
